id App Developer<\/h4>\n                        <\/div>\n                                            <div class=\"item\">\n                            <h4>Desktop App Developer<\/h4>\n                        <\/div>\n                                            <div class=\"item\">\n                            <h4>Malware Analyst<\/h4>\n                        <\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n                                <h1>Sibidharan Nandhakumar<\/h1>\n                <p>Started programming at the age of 12, I got a keen interest towards Cyber Security and have explored multiple dimensions of it. As college dropout, I took the road of Entrepreneurship and progressively worked with multiple companies and startups on multiple technologies ranging from software to security to hardware, which gave me a brief exposure towards the industry. You can contact me for a coffee or to get your idea into code or to consult for your software, security or hardware needs. <br><br> <a href=\"\/about-me\" class=\"btn btn-primary\"> Know More<\/a> <a href=\"\/learn-hacking\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Learn Hacking<\/a> <hr style=\"border: 1px solid #007ced\"> <a href=\"http:\/\/www.instagram.com\/sibidharan\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn \" style=\"color: white\"><i class=\"fa fa-instagram\"><\/i> Follow me on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n\t<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"fw-main-row  \"  >\n\t<div class=\"fw-container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\r\n\r\n<div class=\" col-xs-12 col-sm-12 \">\r\n    <div id=\"col_inner_id-65c2516b373b0\" class=\"fw-col-inner\" data-paddings=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\">\r\n\t\t\n\t<div class=\"fw-divider-space\" style=\"padding-top: 50px;\"><\/div>\n\t<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\t\r\n\r\n<div class=\" col-xs-12 col-sm-12 \">\r\n    <div id=\"col_inner_id-65c2516b3741e\" class=\"fw-col-inner\" data-p